---
import Layout from '~/layouts/PageLayout.astro';

const metadata = {
  title: 'Science-led education for aging skin changes',
  ignoreTitleTemplate: true,
};
---

<Layout metadata={metadata}>
  <section class="px-4 sm:px-6 py-14 sm:py-20 mx-auto max-w-6xl">
    <p class="text-sm font-medium text-accent mb-4">Science-led education for skin and scent changes after 60</p>
    <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight text-default max-w-4xl">
      This Is Not About Hygiene. This Is About What Changes in Your Skin After 60.
    </h1>
    <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-muted max-w-3xl">
      If your routine feels less effective than it used to, you are not doing anything wrong. Aging skin can change at a
      biological level, and those changes may affect how products behave.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-6 text-sm font-medium text-default/90">
      MD, PhD in Biophysics | 30+ Years in Pharmaceutical R&amp;D | Delivery Systems Innovator
    </p>
    <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3">
      <a class="btn-primary" href="#guide">Get the Free Guide</a>
      <a class="btn-secondary" href="#education">Start Here</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="px-4 sm:px-6 py-12 mx-auto max-w-6xl border-t border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800">
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight">A Different Way to Think About Skin</h2>
    <p class="mt-4 text-muted max-w-3xl">
      Most skincare advice treats skin like a surface problem. Dr. Lurie approaches skin as a dynamic biological
      system—one that can change with age, environment, and daily stress.
    </p>
    <ul class="mt-6 space-y-2 text-default list-disc pl-5">
      <li>This is not a cleanliness issue</li>
      <li>This is not about using increasingly harsh products</li>
      <li>This is about why long-standing routines may stop feeling effective</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="px-4 sm:px-6 py-12 mx-auto max-w-6xl">
    <h2 class="sr-only">Entry points</h2>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <article class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800 p-6 bg-white dark:bg-slate-900">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">Understand What May Be Changing</h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-muted">
          Learn how aging skin biology can influence comfort, scent, and how products perform over time.
        </p>
        <a class="mt-5 inline-flex font-medium text-primary hover:text-secondary" href="#insights">Start Learning →</a>
      </article>
      <article class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800 p-6 bg-white dark:bg-slate-900">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">Explore Future Science-Led Solutions</h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-muted">
          See how age-aware formulation principles can guide better next-generation products.
        </p>
        <a class="mt-5 inline-flex font-medium text-primary hover:text-secondary" href="#early-access"
          >See the Approach →</a
        >
      </article>
      <article class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800 p-6 bg-white dark:bg-slate-900">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">Follow a Structured Path</h3>
        <p class="mt-3 text-muted">Use a clear educational framework to move from confusion to practical next steps.</p>
        <a class="mt-5 inline-flex font-medium text-primary hover:text-secondary" href="#guide">Explore the System →</a>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="px-4 sm:px-6 py-12 mx-auto max-w-6xl border-t border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800">
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight">You May Be Doing Everything Right…</h2>
    <ul class="mt-5 space-y-2 list-disc pl-5">
      <li>You shower regularly</li>
      <li>You choose quality products</li>
      <li>You stay consistent with your routine</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="mt-6 font-semibold">And yet…</p>
    <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 list-disc pl-5">
      <li>Your skin may feel different</li>
      <li>Products may seem to fade in usefulness</li>
      <li>Scent and comfort can shift quietly over time</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="mt-6 text-lg font-medium">Most people are never told why this can happen.</p>
  </section>

  <section id="education" class="px-4 sm:px-6 py-12 mx-auto max-w-6xl">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-start">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight">What Can Change With Age</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-muted">
          Aging may influence several connected systems at once, which is why surface-level fixes are often incomplete.
        </p>
        <ul class="mt-5 space-y-2 text-default list-disc pl-5">
          <li>Lipid composition may shift</li>
          <li>Skin barrier function can become less resilient</li>
          <li>Microbial balance may change</li>
          <li>Scent-related compound formation can shift, including 2-nonenal</li>
        </ul>
        <a class="mt-6 inline-flex font-medium text-primary hover:text-secondary" href="#guide"
          >Get the full explanation in the free guide →</a
        >
      </div>
      <aside
        class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800 p-5 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-slate-900"
        aria-label="Skin system layers"
      >
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">Skin System Layers (Simplified)</h3>
        <ol class="mt-4 space-y-3">
          <li class="rounded-lg bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 px-4 py-3 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
            Surface
          </li>
          <li class="rounded-lg bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 px-4 py-3 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
            Lipid layer
          </li>
          <li class="rounded-lg bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 px-4 py-3 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
            Microbial environment
          </li>
          <li class="rounded-lg bg-white dark:bg-slate-800 px-4 py-3 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
            Barrier function
          </li>
        </ol>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="guide" class="px-4 sm:px-6 py-12 mx-auto max-w-6xl border-t border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800">
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight">The Senior’s Guide to Aging Skin &amp; Body Odor</h2>
    <p class="mt-4 text-muted max-w-3xl">
      A practical, science-led primer to help you understand what may be changing, why it matters, and how to avoid
      common mistakes driven by generic hygiene advice.
    </p>
    <ul class="mt-5 space-y-2 list-disc pl-5">
      <li>Why skin can behave differently after 60</li>
      <li>What standard products often overlook</li>
      <li>What to know about age-related scent changes</li>
      <li>How to choose next steps with more confidence</li>
    </ul>
    <form class="mt-8 max-w-xl" aria-label="Free guide signup form">
      <label for="guide-email" class="block text-sm font-medium">Email address</label>
      <input
        id="guide-email"
        name="email"
        type="email"
        required
        autocomplete="email"
        class="mt-2 py-3 px-4 block w-full text-md rounded-lg border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-700 bg-white dark:bg-slate-900"
        placeholder="you@example.com"
      />
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-muted">We’ll send the guide and occasional educational updates. No spam.</p>
      <button type="submit" class="btn-primary mt-4">Download Free Guide</button>
    </form>
  </section>

  <section class="px-4 sm:px-6 py-12 mx-auto max-w-6xl">
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight">A Different Kind of Solution</h2>
    <p class="mt-4 text-muted">If the system has changed, the solution must change too.</p>
    <ul class="mt-5 space-y-2 list-disc pl-5">
      <li>Designed to work with biological function</li>
      <li>Built for the realities of aging skin behavior</li>
      <li>Grounded in delivery-system science</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section id="early-access" class="px-4 sm:px-6 py-12 mx-auto max-w-6xl border-t border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800">
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight">Currently in Development</h2>
    <p class="mt-4 text-lg font-medium">Deodorant cream for aging-related odor.</p>
    <p class="mt-3 text-muted max-w-3xl">
      Not a stronger deodorant. A different approach to scent formation in aging skin, currently being refined for
      real-world use.
    </p>
    <a class="btn-primary mt-6" href="#guide">Join Early Access List</a>
  </section>

  <section class="px-4 sm:px-6 py-12 mx-auto max-w-6xl">
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight">Built on Medical &amp; Scientific Systems Thinking</h2>
    <ul class="mt-5 space-y-2 list-disc pl-5">
      <li>MD + PhD in Biophysics</li>
      <li>30+ years in pharmaceutical R&amp;D</li>
      <li>Internationally patented delivery-system work</li>
      <li>Experience from concept → clinical → product</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="mt-5 text-sm text-muted">Educational content only. Not medical advice.</p>
  </section>

  <section id="insights" class="px-4 sm:px-6 py-12 mx-auto max-w-6xl border-t border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800">
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight">Start With These Insights</h2>
    <p class="mt-4 text-muted max-w-3xl">
      Editorial topics designed to help you understand the biology before choosing products.
    </p>
    <div class="mt-6 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
      {
        [
          'Why Body Odor Changes After 60',
          'What Is 2-Nonenal — And Why It Matters',
          'Why “Stronger” Products Often Fail',
          'The Truth About Anti-Aging Claims',
          'What Your Skin Is Actually Doing Now',
        ].map((title) => (
          <article class="rounded-xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800 p-4 bg-white dark:bg-slate-900">
            <h3 class="font-semibold">{title}</h3>
          </article>
        ))
      }
    </div>
    <a class="mt-6 inline-flex font-medium text-primary hover:text-secondary" href="/blog">Read More Insights →</a>
  </section>

  <section id="quiz" class="px-4 sm:px-6 py-12 mx-auto max-w-6xl">
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight">What Is Your Skin Trying to Tell You?</h2>
    <p class="mt-4 text-muted max-w-3xl">
      A short quiz to help identify which educational path may be most relevant to you. Results will require email.
      (Placeholder flow for now; backend not enabled yet.)
    </p>
    <a class="btn-secondary mt-6" href="#guide">Take the 2-Minute Quiz</a>
  </section>

  <section class="px-4 sm:px-6 py-12 mx-auto max-w-6xl border-t border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800">
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight">What People Often Want Back</h2>
    <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-muted">Expectation-style examples, not customer testimonials.</p>
    <div class="mt-6 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
      <article class="rounded-xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800 p-5 bg-white dark:bg-slate-900">
        <p>Confidence in daily routines.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="rounded-xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800 p-5 bg-white dark:bg-slate-900">
        <p>A cleaner-feeling approach without harsher habits.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="rounded-xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800 p-5 bg-white dark:bg-slate-900">
        <p>A subtle change that can make daily life feel easier.</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="px-4 sm:px-6 py-12 mx-auto max-w-6xl">
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight">Understand Your Skin — Step by Step</h2>
    <p class="mt-3 text-muted">
      Weekly insights from Dr. Lurie on aging skin, formulation science, and practical next steps.
    </p>
    <form class="mt-6 max-w-xl" aria-label="Newsletter signup form">
      <label for="newsletter-email" class="block text-sm font-medium">Email address</label>
      <input
        id="newsletter-email"
        name="email"
        type="email"
        required
        autocomplete="email"
        class="mt-2 py-3 px-4 block w-full text-md rounded-lg border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-700 bg-white dark:bg-slate-900"
        placeholder="you@example.com"
      />
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-muted">Join the newsletter for educational updates and new resources.</p>
      <button type="submit" class="btn-primary mt-4">Join the Newsletter</button>
    </form>
  </section>

  <section class="px-4 sm:px-6 py-14 mx-auto max-w-6xl border-t border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800">
    <h2 class="sr-only">Final close</h2>
    <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-medium max-w-4xl">
      Most people try to fix the surface. But the system has already changed. Once you understand that, everything else
      becomes clearer.
    </p>
    <a class="btn-primary mt-8" href="#guide">Get the Free Guide</a>
  </section>
</Layout>
